Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.29,0:00:28.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}走自己的路 莫要阻拦
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.00,0:00:30.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}迈向巅峰
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.53,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}昂首挺胸 因为我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}为我骄傲的人生
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.47,0:00:36.72,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别跟我谈规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}让我住手？ 想限制我就是徒劳
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.22,0:00:44.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}震耳欲聋 此刻扳机声响起
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}小子 你很张狂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.32,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}感觉不会输
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.40,0:00:53.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别停 装填决心的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.74,0:00:58.83,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}瞄准目标 莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.12,0:01:02.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.25,0:01:06.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.28,0:01:10.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.12,0:01:12.30,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}不可阻挡 不受干扰气势
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.34,0:01:18.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}随手颠覆你的想象
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.64,0:01:20.48,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}周而复始 浴火重生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.48,0:01:21.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}招惹我会付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}向描绘的未来前行而已
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.72,0:01:33.03,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.03,0:01:36.16,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.00,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.00,0:01:41.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
